title: Divi 3.12.2 - WordPress Theme by ElegantThemes
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Divi WordPress Theme is powered by the Divi Builder, an insanely fast and incredibly intuitive front end editor like nothing you have seen before. It will change the way you build websites forever. Divi Theme comes with over 20 pre-made layouts right out of the box. These beautiful layouts can be used to jump-start your new projects, allowing you to build new pages in just a matter of minutes. Load them up, swap out the content and you are good to go! They are also a great way for new customers to learn the ins and outs of the Divi Builder Plugin. Pre-made Divi WordPress Theme Layouts of your own can be saved to your Divi Library for later and then loaded instantly on new pages. Build up your library with your favorite layouts and use them to save hours of time on your future client projects. It’s like having hundreds of themes in one! With Divi WordPress Theme Nulled, you can build just about anything. It’s the most versatile theme we have ever built and quite possible the only theme you will ever need. Divi is one of the only themes to offer a comprehensive roles system. Limit what your clients can do in the Divi Builder to prevent them from messing up your design! Divi WordPress Template comes with a plethora of header options that allow you build really unique looking websites. Choose between a left aligned or centered logo. Switch between vertical and horizontal navigation. Adjust colors, enable transparent headers or opt to hide your navigation before scrolling. There are even full screen and slide-in navigation styles that work great on mobile! Divi WordPress Theme Features Tons Of Header & Footer Options An Intuitive Theme Options Panel Smart Split Testing Powerful Stats & Insights Translated Into 32 Languages Right-To-Left (RTL) Support Rock Solid Security
